53
00:04:19.259 --> 00:04:23.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ああ あれね 借金返すために
とっくに売っちまった

54
00:04:24.764 --> 00:04:27.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
