86
00:06:19.670 --> 00:06:23.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ウナギ スッポン マムシ ニンニク
朝鮮人参

87
00:06:23.174 --> 00:06:27.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
