下痢はするし

90
00:06:31.933 --> 00:06:33.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（山岡）
そりゃ当たり前ですよ

91
00:06:34.477 --> 00:06:35.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ええ？

92
00:06:37.146 --> 00:06:40.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
夏バテが一番影響するのは
胃と腸です

93
00:06:40.775 --> 00:06:43.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
