94
00:06:43.444 --> 00:06:46.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
そこへウナギやマムシみたいな
強い食べ物を食べても―

95
00:06:46.906 --> 00:06:49.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
